The paper deals with image forgery detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). It also mentions the use of deep learning (cs.MM) and the vulnerability of CNNs to adversarial attacks (cs.CR). The paper proposes a method to analyze the vulnerability of CNN-based image forgery detectors, which involves testing performance on a wide range of manipulations (cs.LG) and considering several types of attack (cs.AI).
